  "texts": [
    "They may also serve to advise on domain-specific LLMs built from foundational models, for example, if the LLM is targeting an actuarial use case.",
    "The Geneva Association (2018)",
    "\"To comply with the purpose specification rule, entities striving to engage in big data analysis will need to inform their data subjects of the future forms of processing they will engage in (which must still be legitimate by nature) and closely monitor their practices to assure they do not exceed the permitted realm of analyses.",
    "Carrying out any one of these tasks might prove costly, difficult, or even impossible.",
    "In practice, much depends on how these principles are applied."
